HEADWORD: Proletarian
<hw>Prol`e*ta"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>proletarius</ets>. See Proletary.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
the proletaries; belonging to the commonalty; hence, mean; vile;
vulgar.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Every citizen, if he were not a
<xex>proletarian</xex> animal kept at the public cost.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>De
Quincey.</au> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A proletary.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proletariat</ent>⟦br⟧
